      "id": "PopularPost59616",
      "post_content": "It's rated so low because it's definitely no red [Doom Blade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doom Blade). It's sorcery speed, it's a aura, (meaning if your opponent has enchantment destruction they can save their creature) and lastly it doesn't help you at all if you try to play it on a creature that your opponent is already smacking you with in the first place. It's only real use is playing it on a wall or a creature that your opponent is just using for the ability, and in which case [Lightning Bolt](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt) can usually do the job.",
      "posted_by": "BrutalJim",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost59616\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">It's rated so low because it's definitely no red <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Doom Blade\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doom Blade\">Doom Blade</a>. It's sorcery speed, it's a aura, (meaning if your opponent has enchantment destruction they can save their creature) and lastly it doesn't help you at all if you try to play it on a creature that your opponent is already smacking you with in the first place. It's only real use is playing it on a wall or a creature that your opponent is just using for the ability, and in which case <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Lightning Bolt\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lightning Bolt\">Lightning Bolt</a> can usually do the job.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '59616'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2008\">BrutalJim</span>\r\n                                (3/12/2010 5:46:53 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubCont