    {
      "id": "PopularPost363932",
      "post_content": "An effect with such a highly conditional use should either be a cantrip or at least cost ![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol) only.  \n  \n[Bloodshed Fever](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bloodshed Fever) is *almost* strictly better:  \n  \nThis effect is usually even worse than just making the creature attack no matter what, since your opponent gets the choice to use the enchanted creature for something else one last turn instead.  \n  \nThe only exception to this is if you enchant a creature that *can't attack*, like creatures with defender.",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost363932\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">An effect with such a highly conditional use should either be a cantrip or at least cost <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/> only.<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Bloodshed Fever\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bloodshed Fever\">Bloodshed Fever</a> is <i>almost</i> strictly better:<br/><br/>This effect is usually even worse than just making the creature attack no matter what, since your opponent gets the choice to use the enchanted creature for something else one last turn instead.<br/><br/>The only exception to this is if you enchant a creature that <i>can't attack</i>, like creatures with defender.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '363932'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\">Mode</span>\r\n                                (2/16/2014 3:11:37 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainCon